[SPEAKER_01] oči Paveli povijeti prezentaciju.

1197
01:22:43,060 --> 01:22:44,560
[SPEAKER_01] To, to, to, to, to, to.

1198
01:22:44,560 --> 01:22:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] Moli vas ako treba,

1199
01:22:45,420 --> 01:22:46,239
[SPEAKER_01] nemojte spavat.

1200
01:22:46,239 --> 01:22:47,640
[SPEAKER_01] To mi napravite do ujutru.

1201
01:22:47,640 --> 01:22:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] I ode ta osoba doma

1202
01:22:51,920 --> 01:22:53,220
[SPEAKER_01] i cijelu noć to rad donese.

1203
01:22:53,220 --> 01:22:54,619
[SPEAKER_01] I dođe ujutru do donese

1204
01:22:54,619 --> 01:22:55,819
[SPEAKER_01] i kare direktor.

1205
01:22:55,819 --> 01:22:56,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ma joj, dobro,

1206
01:22:56,500 --> 01:22:57,579
[SPEAKER_01] odgodili smo taj sastavak

1207
01:22:57,579 --> 01:22:58,659
[SPEAKER_01] najmeze bit će drugi put.

1208
01:22:58,659 --> 01:23:01,899
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ste nju tako uvrijedli.

1209
01:23:01,899 --> 01:23:05,340
[SPEAKER_01] Toliko ste fulali njezini život.

1210
01:23:05,340 --> 01:23:07,680
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, morate vi oprezni biti s njom.

1211
01:23:07,680 --> 01:23:08,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ako znaš da je takva.

1212
01:23:08,659 --> 01:23:10,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ne smiješ joj tako nešto dati

1213
01:23:10,840 --> 01:23:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] da su tada nam to reklo

1214
01:23:11,960 --> 01:23:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] ne, potrebe, možemo bez toga.

1215
01:23:13,699 --> 01:23:15,199
[SPEAKER_01] A, ne, ne, ne,

1216
01:23:15,199 --> 01:23:16,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa nije spavala cijelu noć.

1217
01:23:16,300 --> 01:23:18,859
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to moraš stano imati na umu.

1218
01:23:18,859 --> 01:23:19,800
[SPEAKER_01] S kim komuniciraš

1219
01:23:19,800 --> 01:23:21,159
[SPEAKER_01] i kome daješ koje zadatke.

1220
01:23:21,159 --> 01:23:22,600
[SPEAKER_00] Za razliku od Rottweiler

1221
01:23:22,600 --> 01:23:23,520
[SPEAKER_00] koji bi rekao u redu,

1222
01:23:23,520 --> 01:23:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] ja idemo dalje.

1223
01:23:24,340 --> 01:23:25,640
[SPEAKER_01] Da, pa joj da idemo u redu.

1224
01:23:25,640 --> 01:23:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje je problem?

1225
01:23:26,260 --> 01:23:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] Znate ko je dobar, Labrador.

1226
01:23:28,619 --> 01:23:30,520
[SPEAKER_01] To je predivan pas.

1227
01:23:30,520 --> 01:23:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] Primjer jedan.

1228
01:23:32,659 --> 01:23:34,619
[SPEAKER_01] Dođete, imate dućan skladišta.

1229
01:23:34,619 --> 01:23:35,760
[SPEAKER_01] Rezerni dijelova.

1230
01:23:36,340 --> 01:23:37,340
[SPEAKER_01] I dođe jedna gospođa.

1231
01:23:37,340 --> 01:23:40,560
[SPEAKER_01] I ovaj, sineki, tako bi trebalo ovaj ventil,

1232
01:23:40,560 --> 01:23:42,300
[SPEAKER_01] mašina mi nekaj neštima,

1233
01:23:42,300 --> 01:23:43,020
[SPEAKER_01] bute mi dali.

1234
01:23:43,020 --> 01:23:46,020
[SPEAKER_01] Gospođo, to je rijedak ventila,

1235
01:23:46,020 --> 01:23:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] bute, bez griga ja ću ga naći.

1236
01:23:47,380 --> 01:23:50,340
[SPEAKER_01] I taj koji to radi za tim pultom

1237
01:23:50,340 --> 01:23:51,520
[SPEAKER_01] ili prostor,

1238
01:23:51,520 --> 01:23:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] ode u skladište,

1239
01:23:52,800 --> 01:23:54,220
[SPEAKER_01] nema ga 10 minuta,

1240
01:23:54,220 --> 01:23:54,979
[SPEAKER_01] nema ga 15 minuta.

1241
01:23:54,979 --> 01:23:55,760
[SPEAKER_01] Donese li to taj,

1242
01:23:55,760 --> 01:23:56,859
[SPEAKER_01] ne, nije taj,

1243
01:23:56,859 --> 01:23:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] daj ću, budem ja drugi.

1244
01:23:57,960 --> 01:23:59,300
[SPEAKER_01] A iza ove, gospođe,

1245
01:23:59,300 --> 01:24:00,319
[SPEAKER_01] još se pravi red.

1246
01:24:00,319 --> 01:24:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] 5,6 ljudi čeka.

1247
01:24:01,420 --> 01:24:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ovaj se ubi da ti nađe taj ventil.

1248
01:24:04,000 --> 01:24:06,819
[SPEAKER_01] On potoši pola sata,

1249
01:24:06,819 --> 01:24:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] a skladište red se napravio.

1250
01:24:08,840 --> 01:24:10,520
[SPEAKER_01] I ništa nije riješio.

1251
01:24:10,520 --> 01:24:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa pute mi dali telefon,

1252
01:24:11,960 --> 01:24:12,699
[SPEAKER_01] pa ova se ja nazvam.

1253
01:24:12,699 --> 01:24:14,260
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Rotvaller,

1254
01:24:14,260 --> 01:24:15,859
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je ovo, Labrador.

1255
01:24:15,859 --> 01:24:16,859
[SPEAKER_01] Nije za tu funkciju.

1256
01:24:16,859 --> 01:24:18,640
[SPEAKER_01] On mora energično,

1257
01:24:18,640 --> 01:24:19,319
[SPEAKER_01] brzo rješavati.

1258
01:24:19,319 --> 01:24:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] Gospođe, javite se,

1259
01:24:20,199 --> 01:24:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] mi ćemo, naćemo, dopćemo.

1260
01:24:21,199 --> 01:24:22,460
[SPEAKER_01] A ne samo vi čekajte.

1261
01:24:22,460 --> 01:24:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, njega ne.

1262
01:24:24,659 --> 01:24:26,380
[SPEAKER_01] On strašno puno se trudi,

1263
01:24:26,380 --> 01:24:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije dao rezultat.

1264
01:24:27,699 --> 01:24:29,319
[SPEAKER_01] I vi kad zbrojite njegovu

1265
01:24:29,319 --> 01:24:31,060
[SPEAKER_01] eficiency, utjecao,

1266
01:24:31,060 --> 01:24:32,100
[SPEAKER_01] efikasnost rada,

1267
01:24:32,100 --> 01:24:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] puno vremena pozvašio,

1268
01:24:33,500 --> 01:24:34,199
[SPEAKER_01] ništa nije napravio.

1269
01:24:34,199 --> 01:24:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] Da puno zuje,

1270
01:24:34,920 --> 01:24:35,720
[SPEAKER_01] malo meda daje.

1271
01:24:35,720 --> 01:24:37,439
[SPEAKER_01] Da, recimo, to je taj.

1272
01:24:37,439 --> 01:24:39,279
[SPEAKER_01] I onda imate, recimo,

1273
01:24:39,279 --> 01:24:39,720
[SPEAKER_01] basata.

1274
01:24:39,720 --> 01:24:40,399
[SPEAKER_01] To je onaj,

1275
01:24:40,399 --> 01:24:40,920
[SPEAKER_01] znači ono je tamo.

1276
01:24:40,920 --> 01:24:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] Onaj s dugim ušima.

1277
01:24:42,039 --> 01:24:43,819
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, ako imate

1278
01:24:43,819 --> 01:24:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] takvog šefa, direktora,

1279
01:24:45,079 --> 01:24:47,619
[SPEAKER_01] i dođete njemu,

1280
01:24:47,619 --> 01:24:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] i on, joj, kak me ovdje nešto probava,

1281
01:24:50,119 --> 01:24:51,819
[SPEAKER_01] sinoj, sam tako loše spavao,

1282
01:24:54,659 --> 01:24:56,640
[SPEAKER_01] točno je sastanak 4-5 ljudi,

1283
01:24:56,640 --> 01:24:58,220
[SPEAKER_01] i on kaje, pa nešto mi ovdje ovdje u uho,

1284
01:24:58,220 --> 01:24:59,439
[SPEAKER_01] nešto mi zubio ovdje,

1285
01:24:59,439 --> 01:25:01,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali ova mi noga opet nije.

1286
01:25:01,260 --> 01:25:02,819
[SPEAKER_01] E sad vi morate s njim nastaviti,

1287
01:25:02,819 --> 01:25:04,180
[SPEAKER_01] kak se iz taj situacija izvuče.

1288
01:25:04,180 --> 01:25:05,800
[SPEAKER_01] Morate početi,

1289
01:25:05,800 --> 01:25:07,060
[SPEAKER_01] to se zove go with flow,

1290
01:25:07,060 --> 01:25:09,020
[SPEAKER_01] ideti sa flow-om,

1291
01:25:09,020 --> 01:25:11,399
[SPEAKER_01] sa tim tokom njegovih misli,

1292
01:25:11,399 --> 01:25:12,600
[SPEAKER_01] i ovo i mene,

1293
01:25:12,600 --> 01:25:14,060
[SPEAKER_01] znate što, mene isto ovdje,

1294
01:25:14,060 --> 01:25:14,640
[SPEAKER_01] i vas isto,

1295
01:25:14,640 --> 01:25:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] i mene isto ovdje počeo,

1296
01:25:16,079 --> 01:25:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] a ja sam si popio,

1297
01:25:17,119 --> 01:25:18,359
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, brufen, tabletu,

1298
01:25:18,359 --> 01:25:20,100
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam drugo covek odma,

1299
01:25:20,460 --> 01:25:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] i odma i njega uvjeri,

1300
01:25:21,460 --> 01:25:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] da će biti i njemu bolje,

1301
01:25:22,699 --> 01:25:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] da on prestane više govorit o svojoj bolesti.

1302
01:25:24,659 --> 01:25:28,220
[SPEAKER_01] Protivnom što ga ti više podupriješ,

1303
01:25:28,220 --> 01:25:29,060
[SPEAKER_01] joj daj, ne, ne,

1304
01:25:29,060 --> 01:25:30,880
[SPEAKER_01] od to odma uzimte to.

1305
01:25:30,880 --> 01:25:32,300
[SPEAKER_00] Sada će vas odma slikovito pitati,

1306
01:25:32,300 --> 01:25:33,600
[SPEAKER_00] koju pasminu najviše volite,

1307
01:25:33,600 --> 01:25:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] od koje najviše zazirete.

1308
01:25:34,920 --> 01:25:37,800
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja sam prihvaćao za sve pasmine,

1309
01:25:37,800 --> 01:25:40,119
[SPEAKER_01] jer sam se naučio s ljudima rati,

1310
01:25:40,119 --> 01:25:40,760
[SPEAKER_01] ja to volim,

1311
01:25:40,760 --> 01:25:42,119
[SPEAKER_01] ali jedino možda,

1312
01:25:42,119 --> 01:25:43,760
[SPEAKER_01] arogancija je najgora.

1313
01:25:43,760 --> 01:25:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] Imate arogantne pasmina,

1314
01:25:45,880 --> 01:25:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] arogantni,

1315
01:25:46,659 --> 01:25:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] nju samo morate pustiti,

1316
01:25:48,140 --> 01:25:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] vremenska da nepogoda prođe.

1317
01:25:50,039 --> 01:25:52,119
[SPEAKER_01] Da se ispuše.

1318
01:25:52,119 --> 01:25:53,020
[SPEAKER_01] Da se ispuše.

1319
01:25:53,020 --> 01:25:54,220
[SPEAKER_01] Nju samo morate pustiti,

1320
01:25:54,220 --> 01:25:55,520
[SPEAKER_01] ništa kontrirati.

1321
01:25:55,520 --> 01:25:56,640
[SPEAKER_01] Imate odbrize ljudi

1322
01:25:56,640 --> 01:25:57,819
[SPEAKER_01] s kojima samo kajate,

1323
01:25:57,819 --> 01:25:58,779
[SPEAKER_01] da, dobro, imaš pravo,

1324
01:25:58,779 --> 01:25:59,579
[SPEAKER_01] to sam čuo, super.

1325
01:25:59,579 --> 01:26:01,060
[SPEAKER_01] I ništa kontrirati.

1326
01:26:01,060 --> 01:26:02,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ali imate onaj poznati vici,

1327
01:26:02,699 --> 01:26:03,720
[SPEAKER_01] znači kad neko nešto

1328
01:26:03,720 --> 01:26:05,600
[SPEAKER_01] neistinto glupo govori,

1329
01:26:05,600 --> 01:26:06,939
[SPEAKER_01] vi ne smijete njim kontrirati.

1330
01:26:06,939 --> 01:26:09,180
[SPEAKER_01] I sad trebate šutiti,

1331
01:26:09,180 --> 01:26:10,899
[SPEAKER_01] pusti da on završi svoje.

1332
01:26:10,899 --> 01:26:14,600
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su jednu gospođu

1333
01:26:14,600 --> 01:26:16,939
[SPEAKER_01] dobitenicu nobave nagrade za ekonomiju

1334
01:26:16,939 --> 01:26:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] pitali, znači ona je iz Izrela,

1335
01:26:18,800 --> 01:26:22,319
[SPEAKER_01] kako ste uspjeli tako

1336
01:26:22,319 --> 01:26:23,979
[SPEAKER_01] uspiti kad vi govorite

1337
01:26:23,979 --> 01:26:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] da drugi šute oko vas.

1338
01:26:25,039 --> 01:26:26,359
[SPEAKER_01] To sam ja par puta i moj,

1339
01:26:26,359 --> 01:26:27,300
[SPEAKER_01] meni karu sa strane.

1340
01:26:27,300 --> 01:26:29,279
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodinjaki, kako to vode

1341
01:26:29,279 --> 01:26:30,220
[SPEAKER_01] među ovi osam ljudi

1342
01:26:30,220 --> 01:26:31,399
[SPEAKER_01] svi šute kad vi govorite?

1343
01:26:31,399 --> 01:26:34,239
[SPEAKER_01] E tad sam ja tu prvi put

1344
01:26:34,239 --> 01:26:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] čuo tu rečenicu,

1345
01:26:34,960 --> 01:26:35,560
[SPEAKER_01] tu priču.

1346
01:26:35,560 --> 01:26:36,699
[SPEAKER_01] I ona govori,

1347
01:26:36,699 --> 01:26:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] da, ja puno govorim,

1348
01:26:38,079 --> 01:26:38,720
[SPEAKER_01] činjenica je.

1349
01:26:38,840 --> 01:26:40,699
[SPEAKER_01] i tu mogu zahvaliti da me ljudi cijene

1350
01:26:40,699 --> 01:26:41,720
[SPEAKER_01] dvije stvari.

1351
01:26:41,720 --> 01:26:42,439
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo je,

1352
01:26:42,439 --> 01:26:44,359
[SPEAKER_01] kad god treba nešto reći,

1353
01:26:44,359 --> 01:26:45,220
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam to znala reći.

1354
01:26:45,220 --> 01:26:47,520
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad treba šutiti,

1355
01:26:47,520 --> 01:26:49,060
[SPEAKER_01] ja znam šutiti.

1356
01:26:49,060 --> 01:26:52,239
[SPEAKER_01] E znate koja je to stvar?

1357
01:26:52,239 --> 01:26:54,140
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam bio u Americi na školovanju,

1358
01:26:54,140 --> 01:26:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] znate kako je počelo školovanje?

1359
01:26:57,960 --> 01:27:00,319
[SPEAKER_01] Nauči se slušat.

1360
01:27:00,319 --> 01:27:02,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam poznat sada,

1361
01:27:02,659 --> 01:27:03,619
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam na sastanku,

1362
01:27:03,619 --> 01:27:05,359
[SPEAKER_01] ja vas pozorno slušam,

1363
01:27:05,359 --> 01:27:06,479
[SPEAKER_01] što god vi govorite.

1364
01:27:06,479 --> 01:27:09,579
[SPEAKER_01] I to vam je najveći kapital

1365
01:27:09,579 --> 01:27:11,520
[SPEAKER_01] koji možete iz jednog razgovora uzeti.

1366
01:27:11,520 --> 01:27:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] Da slušate pozorno sugovornika,

1367
01:27:14,680 --> 01:27:16,140
[SPEAKER_01] a ne da vi njem uskačete.

1368
01:27:16,140 --> 01:27:17,560
[SPEAKER_01] A, ako on, ne, ne, samo šut,

1369
01:27:17,560 --> 01:27:18,479
[SPEAKER_01] samo šut slušaj.

1370
01:27:18,479 --> 01:27:20,739
[SPEAKER_01] I sve pamti što je rečeno,

1371
01:27:20,739 --> 01:27:22,520
[SPEAKER_01] jer iz toga ćeš ti nastupiti

1372
01:27:22,520 --> 01:27:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] da govoriti što je svoj stav

1373
01:27:23,539 --> 01:27:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] ili svoje mišljenje.

1374
01:27:24,500 --> 01:27:27,300
[SPEAKER_01] I to mi je najvažnija rečenica

1375
01:27:27,300 --> 01:27:28,039
[SPEAKER_01] da je bilo u Americi.

1376
01:27:28,039 --> 01:27:29,199
[SPEAKER_01] Nauči slušat.

1377
01:27:29,199 --> 01:27:32,079
[SPEAKER_01] A to puno znači.

1378
01:27:32,079 --> 01:27:33,439
[SPEAKER_01] Hajde doći do društva,

1379
01:27:33,439 --> 01:27:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] pa ne da vidite ako.

1380
01:27:34,159 --> 01:27:36,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možete uvijek slušati.

1381
01:27:36,100 --> 01:27:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, druga stvar,

1382
01:27:38,039 --> 01:27:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] jako je bitno,

1383
01:27:39,760 --> 01:27:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] poznava dobro povijest,

1384
01:27:42,039 --> 01:27:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] umjetnost,

1385
01:27:43,260 --> 01:27:44,720
[SPEAKER_01] znate koliko to znači.

1386
01:27:44,720 --> 01:27:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] To sam vidio boravkom u inozemstvu.

1387
01:27:47,460 --> 01:27:50,279
[SPEAKER_01] Kad imate, imate puno vi inženjera,

1388
01:27:50,279 --> 01:27:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] struka, dakle, riječnika,

1389
01:27:51,380 --> 01:27:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, okruženje koje smo se mi družili sve.

1390
01:27:54,000 --> 01:27:56,220
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, ojedanpust kužite

1391
01:27:56,220 --> 01:27:57,420
[SPEAKER_01] da odskače neko

1392
01:27:57,420 --> 01:27:58,859
[SPEAKER_01] ko dobro zna povijest.

1393
01:27:58,859 --> 01:28:01,079
[SPEAKER_01] To vam se čini nebitno.

1394
01:28:01,079 --> 01:28:01,979
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim,

1395
01:28:01,979 --> 01:28:03,140
[SPEAKER_01] to je jako bitno.

1396
01:28:03,140 --> 01:28:05,100
[SPEAKER_01] U razborima tog nivora,

1397
01:28:05,100 --> 01:28:06,739
[SPEAKER_01] ili sa predsjednicima uprava,

1398
01:28:06,739 --> 01:28:07,479
[SPEAKER_01] koji su školovan,

1399
01:28:07,479 --> 01:28:08,100
[SPEAKER_01] pa ste ga zbogatiti,

1400
01:28:08,100 --> 01:28:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] vidimo, ovo je došao sa Harvarda,

1401
01:28:09,119 --> 01:28:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je sa Cambridgea,

1402
01:28:09,760 --> 01:28:11,279
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je došao sa, ne znam,

1403
01:28:11,279 --> 01:28:11,800
[SPEAKER_01] Berkeleya,

1404
01:28:11,800 --> 01:28:14,279
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je iz Oxforda.

1405
01:28:14,779 --> 01:28:21,640
[SPEAKER_01] morate znati, pratiti i morate uvijek vi tražiti od njega pitanje s kojim će on pokazati što je on naučio.

1406
01:28:21,640 --> 01:28:23,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ne da vi sad njemu pametujete.

1407
01:28:23,819 --> 01:28:24,739
[SPEAKER_01] Puste,

1408
01:28:24,739 --> 01:28:25,600
[SPEAKER_01] pitajte ga,

1409
01:28:25,600 --> 01:28:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] ali po pitanju vas on prepozna kakav ste vi.

1410
01:28:28,539 --> 01:28:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] To je jako opasno.

1411
01:28:30,539 --> 01:28:33,279
[SPEAKER_01] Jer vi sa pitanjem možete pokazati da vi pojma nemate.

1412
01:28:35,180 --> 01:28:36,399
[SPEAKER_01] Na konferencijama.

1413
01:28:36,399 --> 01:28:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam godišnji na stotinu konferencija po svijetu.

1414
01:28:41,000 --> 01:28:46,680
[SPEAKER_01] Od Hustona, Hongkonga, Tokija, Singapura, Hamburga, Minčina i sad u Hanoveru.

1415
01:28:46,680 --> 01:28:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, stano sam konferencijama.

1416
01:28:48,079 --> 01:28:50,399
[SPEAKER_01] Znate kako se vi možete izblamirati?

1417
01:28:50,399 --> 01:28:54,079
[SPEAKER_01] Vi postavite jedno pitanje, puni sebe, dobroj volji.

1418
01:28:54,079 --> 01:28:57,340
[SPEAKER_01] U biti ovaj srti tako sad shvati, sugovorni da vi pojma nemate.

1419
01:28:57,340 --> 01:28:58,939
[SPEAKER_00] Da ste šuplji kao sir.

1420
01:28:58,939 --> 01:28:59,659
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1421
01:28:59,659 --> 01:29:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] Zato uvijek obažljivo, obazljivo sa postavljanjem pitanja.

1422
01:29:04,800 --> 01:29:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ćete pokazati da nešto znate, morate dobro promisli da li je to tako.

1423
01:29:08,840 --> 01:29:10,220
[SPEAKER_01] I onda postaviš pitanje.

1424
01:29:10,220 --> 01:29:13,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sam ja naučio da nema bolje stvari.

1425
01:29:13,739 --> 01:29:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, neki dan je bila neki dan lani konferencija,

1426
01:29:15,920 --> 01:29:18,060
[SPEAKER_01] dozvijem Varšava ili Bukurešt.

1427
01:29:18,060 --> 01:29:18,699
[SPEAKER_01] Bukurešt.

1428
01:29:18,699 --> 01:29:19,920
[SPEAKER_01] Tri mora.

1429
01:29:19,920 --> 01:29:20,720
[SPEAKER_01] Sjetiva.

1430
01:29:20,720 --> 01:29:25,319
[SPEAKER_01] Konferencija ogromna i sad ovi govore o tehnologiji vodika i sve.

1431
01:29:25,319 --> 01:29:29,260
[SPEAKER_01] I mi je 500 ljudi ima trebala, sigurno.

1432
01:29:29,260 --> 01:29:30,500
[SPEAKER_01] Stručnjaci, svi mogoći.

1433
01:29:30,500 --> 01:29:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] I razvojni projekti koje jesu, ja divnem ruku i dođe onda ovi

1434
01:29:34,420 --> 01:29:35,479
[SPEAKER_01] sa mikrofonom, izvodite.

1435
01:29:35,479 --> 01:29:40,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam sam postao pitanje, nisam vidio nigdje o vašim razgovorima

1436
01:29:40,500 --> 01:29:41,100
[SPEAKER_01] e-metanol.

1437
01:29:41,100 --> 01:29:45,399
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se cijela dorana, znate ovako, okrene.

1438
01:29:45,399 --> 01:29:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] A tko to pita?

1439
01:29:46,659 --> 01:29:48,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vidi, k'o taj pita e-metanolu?

1440
01:29:48,220 --> 01:29:50,220
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao e-metanol, to me interesira.

1441
01:29:50,220 --> 01:29:51,239
[SPEAKER_01] To radimo u Hrvatskoj mi.

1442
01:29:51,239 --> 01:29:52,840
[SPEAKER_01] I onda cijela dorana.

1443
01:29:53,119 --> 01:29:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] I završi taj, dakle, ja sam postao to pitanje.

1444
01:29:54,960 --> 01:29:56,260
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam ja ništa obrazlago.

1445
01:29:56,260 --> 01:29:58,520
[SPEAKER_01] Ne vidim da ste išta rekli o metanolu.

1446
01:29:58,520 --> 01:30:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] Onda oni počnu govoriti kao je, kako da je, ali nikoga nije prijetpomenuo sa mene.

1447
01:30:02,539 --> 01:30:07,979
[SPEAKER_01] I onda vidite, predstavne konferencije, ono, coffee break i svi vama sa list kartama.

1448
01:30:08,859 --> 01:30:12,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ova iz Japana, ova iz Amerike, ova iz Nezakoreje.

1449
01:30:12,859 --> 01:30:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mi razvijamo te djevoje.

1450
01:30:13,880 --> 01:30:15,140
[SPEAKER_01] Pa vi imate, pa vi znate še je to.

1451
01:30:15,140 --> 01:30:16,520
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to u tehnologiju mi radimo.

1452
01:30:16,520 --> 01:30:17,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dajte nazovite nas.

1453
01:30:17,500 --> 01:30:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda vam rating ovako skoči.

1454
01:30:20,000 --> 01:30:23,199
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, pametno postaviti pitanje.

1455
01:30:23,199 --> 01:30:24,260
[SPEAKER_01] Najvažnije.

1456
01:30:24,260 --> 01:30:25,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ne dugo.

1457
01:30:25,100 --> 01:30:26,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ne objašnjavati.

1458
01:30:26,279 --> 01:30:28,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ali opet tu imate jednu zamku.

1459
01:30:28,800 --> 01:30:31,239
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ne smijete doći tamo njima nešto docirat.

1460
01:30:31,239 --> 01:30:34,340
[SPEAKER_01] Jer vi ste dobili priliku da postavite pitanje.

1461
01:30:34,340 --> 01:30:37,359
[SPEAKER_01] A vi uvijek kajate, my question is.

1462
01:30:38,039 --> 01:30:40,439
[SPEAKER_01] I onda malo brazdužite nešto.

1463
01:30:40,439 --> 01:30:42,800
[SPEAKER_01] Da ne bude da ste vi sad njim došli tamo njih učiti.

1464
01:30:42,800 --> 01:30:46,300
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodine Jakiću, tako puno danas ste zapravo dali savjeta.

1465
01:30:46,300 --> 01:30:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sad više neću nikad...

1466
01:30:47,199 --> 01:30:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] Poučena ovim što ste zadnje tri minute govorili.

1467
01:30:49,819 --> 01:30:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sad više neću ništa pitati.

1468
01:30:51,239 --> 01:30:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] Možete slovo.

1469
01:30:51,880 --> 01:30:52,560
[SPEAKER_00] Da se ne izblamiram.

1470
01:30:52,560 --> 01:30:54,439
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto izblamirati možete slovo.

1471
01:30:54,439 --> 01:30:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko puno ste danas toga nam rekli.

1472
01:30:57,420 --> 01:30:59,220
[SPEAKER_00] Što o vašoj zapravo struci.

1473
01:30:59,220 --> 01:31:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, rekla sam energetski ste stručnjak.

1474
01:31:01,880 --> 01:31:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] Što o bogatom životnom iskustvu kojeg ste oplemenili sada i kroz ovu knjigu, autobiografija u sedam slika.

1475
01:31:09,239 --> 01:31:10,300
[SPEAKER_00] I ste li dugo pisali knjigu?

1476
01:31:10,300 --> 01:31:15,180
[SPEAKER_01] Knjigu sam pisao god ne po dana i nisam znao da je tako teško knjigu napisati.

1477
01:31:15,180 --> 01:31:15,500
[SPEAKER_01] Aha.

1478
01:31:15,500 --> 01:31:17,399
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što sve sam pisao.

1479
01:31:17,399 --> 01:31:19,060
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, knjiga je moje autorsko dijelo.

1480
01:31:19,060 --> 01:31:24,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam imao urednicu koja je samo to što sam ja govorio obličila gramatičku formu.

1481
01:31:24,619 --> 01:31:27,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se morao svega sjetiti iz glave.

1482
01:31:27,460 --> 01:31:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, knjiga se je sponjela preko šestotina osoba.

1483
01:31:31,079 --> 01:31:35,640
[SPEAKER_01] Iz glave sam se morao sjetiti svega, svi mojih događaja i opisati sve.

1484
01:31:35,640 --> 01:31:42,680
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo sliko, to je jedna najljepšija sličica je bila kad sam ja iz Londona došao.

1485
01:31:42,680 --> 01:31:49,560
[SPEAKER_01] Na to ono, flower, flower, duža kosa, hlačena zvonce, košlja sa cvjetićima.

1486
01:31:49,560 --> 01:31:51,180
[SPEAKER_01] I dolazim ja u sinj.

1487
01:31:51,180 --> 01:31:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] Imao smo kuću kaša staro.

1488
01:31:53,500 --> 01:31:57,859
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazim ja u sinj, iza gospe, podne, nigdje nikoga.

1489
01:31:57,859 --> 01:32:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] Temperatura, 800 stupnjeva vrućina, nikoga na cesti.

1490
01:32:01,760 --> 01:32:03,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ja izađem da vidim kako taj sinj izgleda.

1491
01:32:04,779 --> 01:32:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] Nam dođe na pijacu, glavni trg svoj pijac.

1492
01:32:06,880 --> 01:32:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dođe na pijacu, ni pasa, kako on sinja nekava, ni pasa nikoga.

1493
01:32:11,380 --> 01:32:15,560
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sebi, Bože moj, kada bi ja morao ovdje živit, ubijop se.

1494
01:32:15,560 --> 01:32:20,220
[SPEAKER_01] I velika gospa čula šta sam ja rekao.

1495
01:32:20,220 --> 01:32:25,579
[SPEAKER_01] I meni pošalje curu koju ja u Zagrebu poznam, Jožanim, Snježanu, tada pijedkovići sinja.

1496
01:32:25,579 --> 01:32:26,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ete.

1497
01:32:28,239 --> 01:32:29,899
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što, hvala vam, najljepša.

1498
01:32:29,899 --> 01:32:31,359
[SPEAKER_00] Brzo nam je proteklo vrijeme.

1499
01:32:31,359 --> 01:32:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] A hvala vam što ste podali.

1500
01:32:32,539 --> 01:32:34,039
[SPEAKER_00] Gotovo sati pa, učini mi se.

1501
01:32:34,039 --> 01:32:34,659
[SPEAKER_01] A je to goći?

1502
01:32:34,659 --> 01:32:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da.

1503
01:32:34,960 --> 01:32:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, vidite kako jema brzo ide.

1504
01:32:36,619 --> 01:32:37,600
[SPEAKER_01] Dosta detalja.

1505
01:32:37,600 --> 01:32:40,979
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ja samo kao zakučak htjel reći, svak ne živi svoj način.

1506
01:32:40,979 --> 01:32:42,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što ga veseli i raduje.

1507
01:32:42,840 --> 01:32:49,060
[SPEAKER_01] Nekto što moguće više koristi, ali mora čovjek se stano školovati i učiti.

1508
01:32:49,060 --> 01:32:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne mogu zamrstiti da neko može biti da se ne uči i školuje.

1509
01:32:52,539 --> 01:32:54,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to dnevno mora biti.

1510
01:32:54,239 --> 01:32:55,340
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to vam je energija i snaga.

1511
01:32:55,340 --> 01:32:59,359
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazi iz toga da vidite šta se događa na tržištu, šta se radi u svijetu.

1512
01:32:59,359 --> 01:33:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] A s druge strane, putovanja na dakšnju.

1513
01:33:02,380 --> 01:33:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam isto po cijelom svijetu svugdje prisutan.

1514
01:33:04,500 --> 01:33:11,979
[SPEAKER_01] Ali u svakom slučaju smatram da život u Hrvatsko je nešto čemu treba težiti i te kako cijenite.

1515
01:33:12,420 --> 01:33:13,300
[SPEAKER_00] To mi se sviđa.

1516
01:33:13,300 --> 01:33:16,579
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja ću vam reći školstva i zdravstva i svega.

1517
01:33:16,579 --> 01:33:18,060
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujte da je Hrvatsko najbolje.

1518
01:33:18,060 --> 01:33:20,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ne to mi je ni zašto.

1519
01:33:20,439 --> 01:33:25,619
[SPEAKER_01] Petru umčad imam, tako da sam uključen i osnovno u školu, gimnaziju, pratimo sve što je.

1520
01:33:25,619 --> 01:33:30,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je činjenica i evo sad posve to...

1521
01:33:30,159 --> 01:33:32,359
[SPEAKER_00] Život u Hrvatskoj ima svoju ljepotu.

1522
01:33:32,359 --> 01:33:34,319
[SPEAKER_01] Definitivno najbolju.

1523
01:33:34,319 --> 01:33:37,920
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ja koji sam živio u Švistarskoj, dalje živim Švistarskoj u Austriji, dalje imam tamo i kretine.

1524
01:33:38,060 --> 01:33:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] Sve, sve to, sve. Dakle, ja mogu zaprati ako ću biti.

1525
01:33:40,380 --> 01:33:43,100
[SPEAKER_01] A ovo da bi li je bio naš Hrvatskoj.

1526
01:33:44,380 --> 01:33:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam na tome što ste s nama podijelili.

1527
01:33:46,380 --> 01:33:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] Molim, hvala vam što ste me pozvali.

1528
01:33:47,840 --> 01:33:51,859
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je ovo jedan onako malo drugačiji podcast nego što smo ga do sad imali.

1529
01:33:51,859 --> 01:33:59,560
[SPEAKER_00] Nadam se, dragi gledatelji, da vam je naš gost iznimnog životnog puta, gospodin Ivica Jakićev, bio zanimljiv.

1530
01:33:59,560 --> 01:34:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ako vam je toliko zanimljiv, uvijek možete naručiti knjigu autobiografije u sedam slika i naučiti nešto iz te knjige, ako nešto nisu danas iz podcasta.

1531
01:34:08,699 --> 01:34:09,739
[SPEAKER_00] Knjiga je priručnik.

1532
01:34:09,739 --> 01:34:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, priručnik za život. Odlično. Dakle, bio je ovo jedan priručnik, odnosno podcast za život.

1533
01:34:15,500 --> 01:34:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] Da, je, točno tako, dobro ste rekli.

1534
01:34:17,159 --> 01:34:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam, najljepše još tako.

1535
01:34:18,420 --> 01:34:24,859
[SPEAKER_00] Dragi naši, hvala vam na pažnji. Vidimo se mi. Vrlo brzo bio ovo još jedan podcast Mrežnica.

